text:
@DPJHodges What Dominic #Cummings "believes" is not relevant. The question is whether #Cummings breached regulation 6 of the The Health Protection (Coronavirus, Restrictions) (England) Regulations 2020 as they stood at the time. 
We don't get to choose what laws to obey?
